I was thinking of ways that verant could possibly spin item decay in EQ2. One way would be to put a duration on the decay itself. Some items decay faster than others, while some do not decay at all being magical in reference. The high end items which would require incredible time sinks, would be done knowing that it would never break, so they would never have to do the quest again. While 80% of the items in EQ would have flucuating decay rates based on their level. <br>
